// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2916 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 8e251b3f-51d5-51eb-957b-a68301f32ffe

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
